BTP_RAP_FINAL_4112

SAP RAP (RESTful ABAP Programming Model) project developed in SAP BTP ABAP Environment as a final backend application.

📌 Project Overview

This project implements a complete Sales Order Management application using:

SAP RAP Managed Scenario
CDS View Entities
Behavior Definitions & Implementations
Fiori Elements UI
OData V4 Services
Validations & Determinations
Parent-Child Composition
SAP BTP ABAP Environment

The application allows users to:

Create Sales Orders
Auto-generate Sales Order IDs
Manage Sales Order Items
Validate business rules
Consume the application through SAP Fiori Elements
🛠 Technologies Used
ABAP RESTful Application Programming Model (RAP)
SAP BTP ABAP Environment
CDS Views
Behavior Definitions
Behavior Implementations
OData V4
SAP Fiori Elements
Eclipse ADT
abapGit
📂 Main Objects
Header Entity
ZI_SO_HEADER_4112
