⚙ Features

✅ Managed RAP Scenario
✅ Parent-Child Composition
✅ Auto-generated Sales Order IDs
✅ Field Validations
✅ Determinations
✅ Fiori Elements UI
✅ OData Service Exposure
✅ CRUD Operations

🚀 How to Run
Open Eclipse ADT
Pull repository using abapGit
Activate all objects
Publish OData Service Binding
Open Fiori Elements Preview
📷 Application Preview
Sales Order List Report
Object Page
